Detailed Description

Minimalistic OSM parser (old and slow).

Only handles the attributes required for this project and ignores everything else.

Note:
This is a old version of the parser which uses QXmlStreamReader. It is therefore standard compliant, but also takes much longer to parse the data (5 to 10 times slower).
